WEBVTT

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:30.880
never provide poor solutions
to poor people.

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:33.016
They are smart.

00:07:33.040 --> 00:07:38.520
(Applause)

00:07:41.320 --> 00:07:42.976
A few months later,

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:45.016
another woman came to the bank --

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:46.576
Kerabai.

00:07:46.600 --> 00:07:50.016
She mortgaged her gold and took the loan.

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:54.736
I asked Kerabai, "Why are you
mortgaging your precious jewelry

00:07:54.760 --> 00:07:56.456
and taking a loan?"

00:07:56.480 --> 00:08:00.456
Kerabai said, "Don't you realize
that it's a terrible drought?